LAMMPS (29 Oct 2020)
units 	metal

variable 	T equal 300
variable 	V equal vol
variable 	dt equal 0.0005
variable 	d equal 200000	# thermo interval

# convert from LAMMPS metal units to SI

variable 	kB equal 1.3806504e-23	 # [J/K] Boltzmann constant
variable 	eV2J equal 1.602176565e-19
variable	ps2s equal 1.0e-12
variable 	A2m equal 1.0e-10

# set up problem
dimension 	3
boundary 	p p s
atom_style atomic

neighbor	2.0 nsq
read_data lammps.txt
Reading data file ...
  orthogonal box = (0.0000000 0.0000000 0.0000000) to (7.6233664 15.246733 141.66809)
  1 by 2 by 32 MPI processor grid
  reading atoms ...
  1840 atoms
  read_data CPU = 0.016 seconds

pair_style mlip mlip.ini
pair_coeff * *

### wrong ###########
#pair_style hybrid lj/cut 12 tersoff/table tersoff/table
#pair_coeff 1 1  tersoff/table SiCGe.tersoff Si(D)  # Tersoff potential must be * *, cannot specify 1 1
#pair_coeff 2 2  tersoff/table newC.tersoff C
#pair_coeff 1 2  lj/cut 0.008909 3.326

#pair_style hybrid lj/cut 8.5 tersoff tersoff
#pair_coeff * * tersoff 1 SiCGe.tersoff Si(D) NULL
#pair_coeff * * tersoff 2 SiCGe.tersoff NULL Ge
#pair_coeff 1 2 lj/cut 0.1664 3.4

# define cold and hot regions

variable 	l_c equal 5.442
variable 	Neach equal 80
variable 	Nedge equal 8
variable 	Nres equal 8
variable 	NSED equal 8
variable 	Nabdon equal 4

variable     posi_leftedge equal 8.0
variable     posi_rightedge equal 133.0
variable     posi_hot equal 45
variable     posi_cold equal 116.0

region 112 block INF INF INF INF INF ${posi_leftedge} units box
region 112 block INF INF INF INF INF 8 units box
group edge_left region 112
64 atoms in group edge_left
region 113 block INF INF INF INF ${posi_rightedge} INF units box
region 113 block INF INF INF INF 133 INF units box
group edge_right region 113
144 atoms in group edge_right
region 114 block INF INF INF INF ${posi_leftedge}  ${posi_rightedge} units box
region 114 block INF INF INF INF 8  ${posi_rightedge} units box
region 114 block INF INF INF INF 8  133 units box
group mid region 114
1632 atoms in group mid

region 2 block INF INF INF INF ${posi_leftedge}  ${posi_hot} units box
region 2 block INF INF INF INF 8  ${posi_hot} units box
region 2 block INF INF INF INF 8  45 units box
group hot region 2
256 atoms in group hot
region 3 block  INF INF INF INF ${posi_cold} ${posi_rightedge} units box
region 3 block  INF INF INF INF 116 ${posi_rightedge} units box
region 3 block  INF INF INF INF 116 133 units box
group cold region 3
342 atoms in group cold

velocity edge_left set  0.0 0.0 0.0
velocity edge_right set 0.0 0.0 0.0

# initial velocity
velocity 	mid create 300 728462 mom yes rot yes dist gaussian
fix 1 mid momentum 1 linear 1 1 1 angular

timestep 	${dt}
timestep 	0.0005
thermo_style    custom step temp press pe ke lx ly lz
thermo	$d
thermo	200000

# ------------- Equilibration and thermalisation ----------------
fix  NVT mid nvt temp $T $T 0.10
fix  NVT mid nvt temp 300 $T 0.10
fix  NVT mid nvt temp 300 300 0.10
dump 1112 all atom 500 nvt.tj #it was npt before
run 	2000000
Neighbor list info ...
  update every 1 steps, delay 10 steps, check yes
  max neighbors/atom: 2000, page size: 100000
  master list distance cutoff = 5.8
  ghost atom cutoff = 5.8
  1 neighbor lists, perpetual/occasional/extra = 1 0 0
  (1) pair mlip, perpetual
      attributes: full, newton on
      pair build: full/nsq
      stencil: none
      bin: none
